# .trivyignore — Accepted / intentional Trivy findings
# --------------------------------------------------------
# Format: <rule-id>  # justification
# See: https://aquasecurity.github.io/trivy/latest/docs/configuration/filtering/

# DS-0002: The Dockerfile *builder* stage runs as root so that uv/pip can
# install packages to /build. The *production* stage explicitly switches to
# a non-root user (appuser, UID 1001) via USER appuser before the entrypoint.
# Trivy cannot distinguish which stage a finding applies to in multi-stage
# builds; the production image is non-root in practice.
DS-0002
